description:
Justice_League_3000_-_Yesterday_Lives_(2014-10)_TPB_(digital)_(OkC.O.M.P.U.T.O.-Novus-HD)


A New 52 volume written by Keith Giffen and J.M. DeMatteis and illustrated by Howard Porter starring the Justice League 1,000 years into the future.

The series was originally announced with Kevin Maguire on art duties, originally to launch in October 2013, but he was removed from the book shortly after the announcement, replaced by Howard Porter who had done the initial character designs, and the title was delayed to December.

Collected Editions

Justice League 3000: Yesterday Lives - collects issues #1-7
